• The Tips window got a whole lot more powerful.

• In the Actions window of Tips, type ‘tracker’ to quickly access the spreadsheet containing links to all of the issue’s work.

• Or type ‘Artwork’ to quickly open the SCJ Artwork folder in the Finder. ‘Guide’ to access the folder with the InDesign file.

• Multiple user accounts on your computer can safely use the SCJ app — each with their own independent progress and settings.

• Log in as the senior designer to disable Adobe compatibility checks.
